description: Main portfolio page with developer information, project descriptions, and contact form. Serves index.html content.
notes: Single-page application with anchor links (#about, #projects, #contact) for navigation. All sections are served from the same HTML document. Contact form uses client-side JavaScript only (event.preventDefault). Sections include: About Us (developers John and Peter), Projects (NAS, Modernizer 200), Contact Form. GET method supported; POST, PUT, DELETE, OPTIONS, PATCH methods not supported.
